<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #007bff;
            
        }
        .innerContainer{
            width: 60%;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .profileContainer{
            flex-direction: column;
            h1{
                color: white;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column-reverse;

            }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #30ceac;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .message {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .user-logo {
            height: 50px;
            width: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .logout-button {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            margin: 20px;
            border: 1px solid white;
        }

        .logout-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            border: none;
        }

        .dummy-content {
            margin-top: 50px;
            color: #777;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .dummy-content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .user-logo {
                height: 40px;
            }

            .logout-button {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .dummy-content {
                padding: 0 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="innerContainer">

            <h1>Welcome <img src="/images/programmer.png" alt="userlogo" class="user-logo"> </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="profileContainer">

            <h1>
                
                <%= user.name %>
                <img src="/images/man.png" alt="userlogo" class="user-logo">
            </h1>
        </div>
        <form action="/logout" method="get">
            <button type="submit" class="logout-button">Logout</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/reset" method="get">
            <button type="submit" class="logout-button">Reset Password</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="dummy-content">
        <p class="message">You are now logged in</p>
        <p>This is some dummy content added to demonstrate the page layout.</p>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla varius eros a lacus accumsan mattis. Fusce quis lacinia ipsum. Nullam sed velit vel enim dictum tincidunt.</p>
        <p>Proin efficitur diam at velit pulvinar, et tristique eros tempus. Ut ac quam ac ipsum congue sodales. Donec hendrerit aliquam ex ac feugiat.</p>
        <p>Sed non suscipit turpis. Ut consectetur justo sit amet enim vestibulum, eget venenatis magna condimentum.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
